reviews:
Overall ~ I wish it wasn’t over a week late! And that I had original packaging so I could return for a heavier blanket
After loads of reviews I finally ordered a weighted blanket. Originally was supposed to be a gift for my daughter, so ordered well in advance. As I watch her birthday get closer and still no blanket, I went out and purchased another one from the store for her.
When this blanket finally arrived (over a week late and I pay for prime!) I decided to keep for myself (kids opened so really no choice) I weigh 115 (kiddo is 110) so ordered the 15 lb blanket, I am sorry to say it is not heavy enough for me. Or her for that mater. And I can’t return as I do not have original packaging.
The blanket it’s self is good. 4”x”4” squares so the beads stay where they are supposed to, the material seems to be decent quality. I order a queen size. So you know, the blanket is not supposed to overhang the bed. Queen size blanket is about a “double bed” size and that is how it is supposed to be.

After waiting over a month for arrival the dress was entirely to big. I did look at the sizing chart and orderd accordingly, yet you could probably fit 2 of me in it.
The packaging looked like it had been Someone’s foot rest, so can’t even make out the address to return.
The title says it all, gripping from start to finish. The in death series is. Fabulous read no matter how many times I have read it.

I purchased a Lego 42095 set as a Christmas present, the remote lights up but the "motor" does not work. We have tried everything. Needless to say I have a very frustrated kid and parents for that matter.

I hate clutter on my counter but the Instapot has a permanent home there. Since purchase I have used daily, roast from rock hard frozen to on the table in under an hour, potatoes perfectly done. I bought bone in chicken cooked in the instapot and was fall of the bone perfect in 30 minutes. I am horrible for never knowing what to make for dinner while still trying to be healthy, a quick google search has me trying new things because with the Instapot it's quick and easy.
Cute little book, 4 in a package I should have read the description better as it is very little (4x4) and only has about 20 pages.
Warm, durable and washable
So glad to see this on prime. Totally addictive
Great book, very engaging, now looking for the next one's.
A little tight fitting, but great quality, and very durable. Did not shrink in the wash witch is helpful

Purchased as a gift, and worked like a charm
Easy to set up and use
Pegs come out so you can adjust size, but don't fall out while working with it. Delivery was very fast
I was hesitant to order boots online but the fit perfectly, are a good quality, the only thing is they have no tread at all.
Great paper, and loads cheaper then the polaroid camera we also have
Was pleasantly surprised with how soft this made hubby's beard. I purchased as a stocking stuffer but will continue to by as it works better then any products I have tried
My daughter uses this as her bag for school, holds a Dell laptop with room for books as well
Make sure you have a spreader. I tried with a credit card and got huge bubbles, reapplied with a 4" drywall spreader and was nice and smooth
Great product, the cups are tricky to clean if you leave them to long. Suggest cleaning as soon as muffins cool
Works well
Exactly as advertised, and a great deal when you have a budding artist for a child
Plenty of space, monthly quick view, and horizontal day spaces. Best planner I have come across
Works amazing for leg pain. I stand for 8+ hours and with these can do it without all the pain
Good fit, fairly true to size arrived quickly

***wow* I wrote a one star review and had a phone call and replacement on its way within 20 min of the review.... Way to go customer service**very disappointed, ordered this for my daughters birthday in August 2018 here it is January 2019 and will no longer hold a charge

review_title: Amazing read hard to put down
reviews: Cynthia writes in a way that brings the characters alive. Fast paced, good read start to finish. Looking forward to more Madeline Dawkins books
The first in the series took me a while to find it but it was a can't but down from the first moment type book, even though I have read many and know how it turns out.
